divs: Sighting DetailsDriving north on US Hwy 83 out of North Platte, i noticed a moving oject going from my right to left on the horizon. It was a sky gray color with some yellow. The object was long about 30 meters and flat like. It had a bulbus nose and flew tieh the nose kind of pointed down. I would guess it was below 1500 feet and was traveling at about 100 mph. It flew in a straignt line to the west out of sight and vanished. It had no visible markings and made no noise.
